Using Docker

Create container:
docker pull ubuntu
docker run -it ubuntu

Commit change:
exit //from docker
docker commit -m "message" <container-id> image-name

Delete image: docker rmi image-name

Run from existing container:
docker exec -it <container-id> bash

Run from existing image:
docker run -it <image-id> //will create a new container

Get images: docker images

Get container: docker ps // and -a for all

Saving docker image as a tar file:
docker save -o <path for generated tar file> <image name>

Load from tar:
docker load -i <path to image tar file>

Pushing Docker image:
docker login -u sahil25dhull
docker tag <image-name> sahil25dhull/<image-name>
docker push sahil25dhull/<image-name>

Pulling docker image:
docker pull sahil25dhull/<image-name>

